%% Query flow — IOC lookup (cache-first) vs ingest write (idempotent upsert)
flowchart TD
    subgraph read["READ: IOC lookup (hot path)"]
        RQ[lookup request] --> NORM[normalize value]
        NORM --> RGET{Redis GET<br/>ioc:type:value}
        RGET -->|hit| RRET[return verdict <10ms]
        RGET -->|miss| RPG[(Postgres index lookup<br/>type, normalized_value)]
        RPG --> RSET[Redis SETEX 10min]
        RSET --> RRET2[return verdict <200ms]
    end
    subgraph write["WRITE: ingest (idempotent)"]
        WQ[feed item] --> WNORM[normalize]
        WNORM --> WUP[(INSERT ... ON CONFLICT DO UPDATE)]
        WUP --> WSRC[(append indicator_sources)]
        WSRC --> WSCORE[recompute confidence]
    end
